    FlinkUserCodeClassLoaders

    static final class FlinkUserCodeClassLoaders.ChildFirstClassLoader
extends java.net.URLClassLoader
    A variant of the URLClassLoader that first loads from the URLs and only after that from the parent.

    URLClassLoader.getResourceAsStream(String) uses getResource(String) internally so we don't override that.

    • 字段详细资料

      • alwaysParentFirstPatterns

        private final java.lang.String[] alwaysParentFirstPatterns
        The classes that should always go through the parent ClassLoader. This is relevant for Flink classes, for example, to avoid loading Flink classes that cross the user-code/system-code barrier in the user-code ClassLoader.
